comments: Markkanen (CHI) makes contact with Russell's (GSW) body during the pick but contact does not affect his ability to disengage from the play.
Burks (GSW) places his arm to Satoransky's (CHI) front during the pick but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) makes contact with Satoransky's (CHI) body during his drive but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Green (GSW) legally contests Markkanen's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Dunn (CHI) wraps Green (GSW) during the pick and dislodges him from his obtain position.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes position in Robinson III's (GSW) path and makes marginal contact during the pick that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) makes contact with LaVine's (CHI) body during shooting motion that affects his drive shot attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes legal position in Dunn's (CHI) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
Russell (GSW) places a hand to LaVine's (CHI) front during his drive but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Green (GSW) establishes legal position in Dunn's (CHI) path and firms up during the hand-off.
Robinson III (CHI) briefly grasps LaVine's (CHI) arm during the rebound but contact does not affect his ability to gather the loose ball.
Markkanen (CHI) makes some contact with Robinson III (GSW) during the pick but contact does not affect his ability to defend through the play.
Robinson III (CHI) makes marginal contact with LaVine's (CHI) body at the start of his drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes incidental contact with Burks' (GSW) arm attempting to make contact with the loose ball.
